<lb ed="B" n="0157a11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="5"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷五</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0157a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">銅井院</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>銅井院<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0157a13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在朝陽門內東城柳樹灣地東去所綂靈谷寺十二里
<lb ed="B" n="0157a14"/>背城面河城下伏道中引水從銅井口溢出達於御溝
<lb ed="B" n="0157a15"/>霖雨後<g ref="#CB06048"/>湧可觀院因井得名雖僻隘不足匹諸中寺
<lb ed="B" n="0157a16"/>而撫檻臨流頗有濠梁之趣所領小剎曰十方律院吉
<lb ed="B" n="0157a17"/>祥菴廻龍菴龍華菴雙橋圓通菴慈憫菴</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0157a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1807" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音堂<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1812" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍堂<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1818" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址貳畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a1822" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址貳畆
<lb ed="B" n="0157a19"/><note place="inline">東至城墻　南至城墻　西至河　北至城墻</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0157a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">古蹟</cb:mulu><head>【古蹟】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">銅井</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0157a2003" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">銅井<note place="inline">水自伏道中來按志義井二一在石子崗七里鋪井<unclear></unclear>鑄有僧慧廣名南唐保大三年置</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0157b" n="0157b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0157b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">十方律院</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>十方律院<note place="inline">即三一菴</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0157b02"/><p xml:id="pB29p0157b0201" style="margin-left:1em">在朝陽門裏相望東城地南去所領銅井院二里係靈
<lb ed="B" n="0157b03"/>谷律堂下院</p>
